{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"XML (可扩展标记语言)","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/XML","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/XML/XML_Introduction\">XML_介绍</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong>可扩展标记语言</strong>是可由<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">文档对象模型 (DOM)</a>严格序列化的一种语言。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"row topicpage-table\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect2\"><dl><dl><dt <=\"\" dl=\"\" id=\"sect3\"></dt></dl></dl></div>\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect4\"><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"xml_介绍\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/XML/XML_Introduction\">XML_介绍</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">Summary: This article introduces the 'eXtensible Markup Language' (XML) and tells of it's uses.XML (Extensible Markup Language)&nbsp;&nbsp;是一种类似于 &nbsp;HTML 的标记语言，但是 XML 没有使用预定义的标记。因此，您可以根据自己的设计需求定义专属于您的标记。这是一种十分有用的可存储、可搜索和可共享的格式存储数据的方法。最重要的是，因为&nbsp;XML 的基本格式是标准化的，所以如果您跨系统或平台共享或传输 XML ，无论是在本地还是在互联网上，接收方仍然可以根据标准化的 XML 语法解析数据。</dd></dl></div>\n    </div><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"可扩展标记语言是可由文档对象模型 (DOM)严格序列化的一种语言。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"XML: Rozszerzalny Język Znaczników","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"XML: Extensible Markup Language","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/xml","github_url":"https://git